{"about_the_game":"Astronimo is a construction platform puzzler that aims to be the most fun you can have in outer space.<br><br>While mining for minerals in the vast reaches of the galaxy, four Hypergiant Inc. employees crash-land on a small planet and become hopelessly stranded. <br><br>In the hopes of reuniting with their fleet, you must help them to cover every inch of the planetary surface, solve puzzles in unique and creative ways, and then build a shuttle and fuel it to launch back into space. <br><br>Astronimo lifts platforming and customisation to the interstellar medium and beyond with a quirky campaign and customisation tools that stretch the bounds of your imagination.<br><br><strong>Chart A Whole Galaxy </strong><br>A fun-filled campaign featuring the Turilla, Acara, Zaroth IV, and Nixnillon planets. As well as four mini-moons and discoveries aplenty!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/Planets.gif?t=1718023101\" /><br><br><strong>Endless Fun with Friends </strong><br>Play co-op with up to three others locally or online and work out how to get back home together with wacky builds, secrets to discover and planets to explore. <br><br>Wave. Play Music. Be a dog in space. Astronimo is all about having fun and sharing memories with friends, old and new.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/Players.gif?t=1718023101\" /><br><br><strong>Compose Cosmos </strong><br>The World Editor provides elaborate tools to build and populate your own planets to an incredible level of detail and share your creations through Steam Workshop. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/World.gif?t=1718023101\" /><br><br><strong>Drag, Drop and Distribute </strong><br>Workshops make crafting the unimaginable easy. If you can think it, then with Astronimo \u2013 you can build it!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/Workshop.gif?t=1718023101\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Virtuoso","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/abfab5054e8e76f1efa1c812b2357e2340a33ee5.jpg"},{"name":"Community Engager","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/c4644e864f66bdd8dc33b4cd3d5ba42c8ebc1f48.jpg"},{"name":"Life Finds a Way!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/6d015599f58f4940e0789a21d6bfff54b184d5c8.jpg"},{"name":"They'll Suspect Nothing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/05fd28ab7ffe61bced712cfcd189e26665b64417.jpg"},{"name":"Beat the Crumbs Out of Each Other","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/01ae74d585fc15d72e9c594a55e7363299c91d77.jpg"},{"name":"Meditate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/30de6f872741f856824235aa598debd6216d8d75.jpg"},{"name":"Two Heads are Better than One","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/bae0ab78bb95eb242fa3015fec527d26bca11020.jpg"},{"name":"CHIP and Builder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/6dda25277e5a1fcfb54f2857fd5c0eee75dc3112.jpg"},{"name":"Bird Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/7e414db7a53048505d68c58f1c5afbfd1ceb47d7.jpg"},{"name":"Kingdom - 3 Crowns?!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1808640/dc909f865e16e6b8b764c4da48d14580619f142b.jpg"}],"total":15},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1808640?t=1718023101","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it